{"tid":1997023,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[文化歷史台]第二講:百年警隊一亞洲最佳之迷","createTime":"2020-05-01T11:02:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-10T15:58:54.000Z","uid":74954,"like":33,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"adb69be04feb060ba79b3c90b1a8b9f6ed0e50ba","tid":1997023,"uid":74954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T11:02:11.000Z","msg":"本題前言:<br />\n 其實一直係連登都見到唔小人有對殖民時期既香港警察有個誤解<br />\n<br />\n特別係對英治時期既警察/香港皇家警察抱有過於良好既感覺，成日話以前皇家香港警察唔會點點點，會點點點，回歸後唔同哂點點點等既言論。<br />\n<br />\n所以想抽一集開講為大家正統番個歷史觀念<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，同埋為大家分析下呢個思想點解會出現。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利伸: 今次片有d長 雖然諗過分2條出 <br />\n<br />\n不過會破壞左百年警隊既一條線落既題材性。希望唔會悶親大家，作為香港人幫大家建立番個正統香港史觀先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n本課第二講:<br />\n百年警隊一亞洲最佳之迷<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/qc9hrusH6vg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fqc9hrusH6vg&d=29ui5Tvv6aczeWgqk0vw172U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=3429c86f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/qc9hrusH6vg</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n本課重點<br />\n1.係傘運前 ，警民關係密切，大多抱以信任既態度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n[2.新生一代以往傘運前相信警察既原因有三]<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2.1基於香港受英國管治既獨特同作為香港人既認同感<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.2受影視文化既嚴重影響，電影將香港警察塑造為英雄神話，抱打不平，令人信以為真<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.3 香港80，90年代影視文化強勢，令港人驕傲以及相信電影中之情節，並對外國人從戲內或戲外指出香港同內地既大不同，導致我地既觀念長期自己幫自己洗腦，認為香港係獨特，所以香港警察都係與眾不同<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H7S9iii.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH7S9iii.jpg&h=5700e8d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n※簡單d講 姐係我地呢班on9日日用意念對住舊時代d狗打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，所以搞到我地對以前既狗有思想錯覺，誤以為係好野。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(第4點再補充)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n-------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n3.香港警察大家所熟悉既黑暗期以為只有60到70年代。例如一講警隊貪污就第一時間只會諗起葛柏。但其實呢個歷史觀念係錯既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LpQKRHU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLpQKRHU.jpg&h=13dc2c80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n-------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n4. 實際上，香港警隊成立176年 ，當中超過8成時間都係黑警，唔係貪就係濫權，雖然貪都係濫權既一種(有機會再講)<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n5.警隊黑歷史有「賄賂」、「收規」、「射鵰」、「大頭綠衣」既諷刺民謠等等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZGbVdSo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZGbVdSo.jpg&h=ae06bc73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AuFSf5J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAuFSf5J.jpg&h=10d3eb72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n立叔言:<br />\n如果唔係黑警近一年咁臭串，我諗我都未必會無啦啦搵咁遠古警隊既歷史 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，片中內容只係警隊黑歷史既冰山一角，因為黑警以前做過既豐功偉績可以講超過一個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n總結:<br />\n<br />\n希望大家唔好對以前由英國管治既警隊抱有太多幻想，唔好對皇家香港警察有咁多美好ff既空間。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為係20世紀英國用左招以華制華，所以警隊好多散仔都係華人，以前警隊對法治濫權既惡習一直遺傳到而家，警隊176年既文化一句講哂，狗改不了吃屎！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e41668d06e2149481da7f516c6cafd05f81df24d","tid":1997023,"uid":74954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T11:02:49.000Z","msg":"推個一推先"},{"pid":"94dbe1f263b8db2a3e0fa22119007fd8fc0137ea","tid":1997023,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T11:05:53.000Z","msg":"最佳貪污<br />\n以前貪污果班，依家咪做晒高層同警署警長"},{"pid":"c96ee7c2b739975b99337fcece746337d3f1bbe2","tid":1997023,"uid":74954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"94dbe1f263b8db2a3e0fa22119007fd8fc0137ea","tid":1997023,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T11:05:53.000Z","msg":"最佳貪污<br />\n以前貪污果班，依家咪做晒高層同警署警長"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T11:16:49.000Z","msg":"最佳貪污係真既<br />\n但後句貪污做哂高層我就有所保留啦<br />\nicac成立果下 再加埋總督大力主持下<br />\n其實係改變左好多 起碼係回歸前都真係收斂哂"},{"pid":"beb154675b67c858e7d2d893e3e4b8d8934406de","tid":1997023,"uid":74954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c96ee7c2b739975b99337fcece746337d3f1bbe2","tid":1997023,"uid":74954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"94dbe1f263b8db2a3e0fa22119007fd8fc0137ea","tid":1997023,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T11:05:53.000Z","msg":"最佳貪污<br />\n以前貪污果班，依家咪做晒高層同警署警長"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T11:16:49.000Z","msg":"最佳貪污係真既<br />\n但後句貪污做哂高層我就有所保留啦<br />\nicac成立果下 再加埋總督大力主持下<br />\n其實係改變左好多 起碼係回歸前都