-02T14:22:10.000Z","msg":"我片入邊有講到唔同例子 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n例如 1897年既警察重大貪污案件 <br />\n<br />\n因為篇文純粹係一個重點 bullet point 加小小解釋"},{"pid":"cbf32b6e3620443afa478d214daefa36249d8283","tid":1997023,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"adb69be04feb060ba79b3c90b1a8b9f6ed0e50ba","tid":1997023,"uid":74954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T11:02:11.000Z","msg":"本題前言:<br />\n 其實一直係連登都見到唔小人有對殖民時期既香港警察有個誤解<br />\n<br />\n特別係對英治時期既警察/香港皇家警察抱有過於良好既感覺，成日話以前皇家香港警察唔會點點點，會點點點，回歸後唔同哂點點點等既言論。<br />\n<br />\n所以想抽一集開講為大家正統番個歷史觀念<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，同埋為大家分析下呢個思想點解會出現。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利伸: 今次片有d長 雖然諗過分2條出 <br />\n<br />\n不過會破壞左百年警隊既一條線落既題材性。希望唔會悶親大家，作為香港人幫大家建立番個正統香港史觀先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n本課第二講:<br />\n百年警隊一亞洲最佳之迷<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/qc9hrusH6vg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fqc9hrusH6vg&d=29ui5Tvv6aczeWgqk0vw172U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=3429c86f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/qc9hrusH6vg</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n本課重點<br />\n1.係傘運前 ，警民關係密切，大多抱以信任既態度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n[2.新生一代以往傘運前相信警察既原因有三]<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2.1基於香港受英國管治既獨特同作為香港人既認同感<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.2受影視文化既嚴重影響，電影將香港警察塑造為英雄神話，抱打不平，令人信以為真<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.3 香港80，90年代影視文化強勢，令港人驕傲以及相信電影中之情節，並對外國人從戲內或戲外指出香港同內地既大不同，導致我地既觀念長期自己幫自己洗腦，認為香港係獨特，所以香港警察都係與眾不同<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H7S9iii.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH7S9iii.jpg&h=5700e8d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n※簡單d講 姐係我地呢班on9日日用意念對住舊時代d狗打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，所以搞到我地對以前既狗有思想錯覺，誤以為係好野。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(第4點再補充)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n-------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n3.香港警察大家所熟悉既黑暗期以為只有60到70年代。例如一講警隊貪污就第一時間只會諗起葛柏。但其實呢個歷史觀念係錯既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LpQKRHU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLpQKRHU.jpg&h=13dc2c80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n-------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n4. 實際上，香港警隊成立176年 ，當中超過8成時間都係黑警，唔係貪就係濫權，雖然貪都係濫權既一種(有機會再講)<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n5.警隊黑歷史有「賄賂」、「收規」、「射鵰」、「大頭綠衣」既諷刺民謠等等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZGbVdSo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZGbVdSo.jpg&h=ae06bc73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AuFSf5J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAuFSf5J.jpg&h=10d3eb72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n立叔言:<br />\n如果唔係黑警近一年咁臭串，我諗我都未必會無啦啦搵咁遠古警隊既歷史 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，片中內容只係警隊黑歷史既冰山一角，因為黑警以前做過既豐功偉績可以講超過一個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n總結:<br />\n<br />\n希望大家唔好對以前由英國管治既警隊抱有太多幻想，唔好對皇家香港警察有咁多美好ff既空間。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為係20世紀英國用左招以華制華，所以警隊好多散仔都係華人，以前警隊對法治濫權既惡習一直遺傳到而家，警隊176年既文化一句講哂，狗改不了吃屎！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T14:36:25.000Z","msg":"現在法證先峰, 機場特警呢些劇集, 都一樣講到警察好好, 好英勇."},{"pid":"40ac01ab6362ff0a429af19be73409213e03e7af","tid":1997023,"uid":204929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T14:39:39.000Z","msg":"光復香港之後, 除咗制度之外， <br />\n<br />\n用返英治時期同樣嘅招數 去印度搵啲錫克教徒做警察， 會唔會有效解決到警暴問題?"},{"pid":"864d6a812c281f670d40156b101c7f2d390fa92f","tid":1997023,"uid":204929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T14:40:37.000Z","msg":"華人劣根性關唔關事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?"},{"pid":"407025b243658c5abef330702a3d90d870edef81","tid":1997023,"uid":74954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cbf32b6e3620443afa478d214daefa36249d8283","tid":1997023,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"adb69be04feb060ba79b3c90b1a8b9f6ed0e50ba","tid":1997023,"uid":74954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T11:02:11.000Z","msg":"本題前言:<br />\n 其實一直係連登都見到唔小人有對殖民時期既香港警察有個誤解<br />\n<br />\n特別係對英治時期既警察/香港皇家警察抱有過於良好既感覺，成日話以前皇家香港警察唔會點點點，會點點點，回歸後唔同哂點點點等既言論。<br />\n<br />\n所以想抽一集開講為大家正統番個歷史觀念<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，同埋為大家分析下呢個思想點解會出現。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利伸: 今次片有d長 雖然諗過分2條出 <br />\n<br />\n不過會破壞左百年警隊既一條線落既題材性。希望唔會悶親大家，作為香港人幫大家建立番個正統香港史觀先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n本課第二講:<br />\n百年警隊一亞洲最佳之迷<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/qc9hrusH6vg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fqc9hrusH6vg&d=29ui5Tvv6aczeWgqk0vw172U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=3429c86f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/qc9hrusH6vg</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n本課重點<br />\n1.係傘運前 ，警民關係密切，大多抱以信任既態度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n[2.新生一代以往傘運前相信警察既原因有三]<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2.1基於香港受英國管治既獨特同作為香港人既認同感<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.2受影視文化既嚴重影響，電影將香港警察塑造為英雄神話，抱打不平，令人信以為真<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.3 香港80，90年代影視文化強勢，令港人驕傲以及相信電影中之情節，並對外國人從戲內或戲外指出香港同內地既大不同，導致我地既觀念長期自己幫自己洗腦，認為香港係獨特，所以香港警察都係與眾不同<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H7S9iii.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH7S9iii.jpg&h=5700e8d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n※簡單d講 姐係我地呢班on9日日用意念對住舊時代d狗打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，所以搞到我地對以前既狗有思想錯覺，誤以為係好野。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(第4點再補充)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n-------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n3.香港警察大家所熟悉既黑暗期以為只有60到70年代。例如一講警隊貪污就第一時間只會諗起葛柏。但其實呢個歷史觀念係錯既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LpQKRHU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLpQKRHU.jpg&h=13dc2c80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n-------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n4. 實際上，香港警隊成立176年 ，當中超過8成時間都係黑警，唔係貪就係濫權，雖然貪都係濫權既一種(有機會再講)<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n5.警隊黑歷史有「賄賂」、「收規」、「射鵰」、「大頭綠衣」既諷刺民謠等等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZGbVdSo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZGbVdSo.jpg&h=ae06bc73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AuFSf5J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAuFSf5J.jpg&h=10d3eb72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n立叔言:<br />\n如果唔係黑警近一年咁臭串，我諗我都未必會無啦啦搵咁遠古警隊既歷史 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，片中內容只係警隊黑歷史既冰山一角，因為黑警以前做過既豐功偉績可以講超過一個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n總結:<br />\n<br />\n希望大家唔好對以前由英國管治既警隊抱有太多幻想，唔好對皇家香港警察有咁多美好ff既空間。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為係20世紀英國用左招以華制華，所以警隊好多散仔都係華人，以前警隊對法治濫權既惡習一直遺傳到而家，警隊176年既文化一句講哂，狗改不了吃屎！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T14:36:25.000Z","msg":"現在法證先峰, 機場特警呢些劇集, 都一樣講到警察好好, 好英勇."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T14:41:54.000Z","msg":"因為你正聚居於cctvb <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d2f106e39c9a784e44054d534338ffd5cfab359","tid":1997023,"uid":41355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df3f1e1194fb397bbec26093dd71807593d51498","tid":1997023,"uid":74954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"edad47ea67a5a66bba3e88857b1ec6513dc32ebc","tid":1997023,"uid":41355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T11:27:42.000Z","msg":"有無多D資料<br />\n你都係講兩句，無context又無例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T14:22:10.000Z","msg":"我片入邊有講到唔同例子 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n例如 1897年既警察重大貪污案件 <br />\n<br />\n因為篇文純粹係一個重點 bullet point 加小小解釋"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T14:45:38.000Z","msg":"原來條片先係重點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2efa5b352ee112d5c79a7953f88ecaeacdaf8a22","tid":1997023,"uid":74954,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"40ac01ab6362ff0a429af19be73409213e03e7af","tid":1997023,"uid":204929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T14:39:39.000Z","msg":"光復香港之後, 除咗制度之外， <br />\n<br />\n用返英治時期同樣嘅招數 去印度搵啲錫克教徒做警察， 會唔會有效解決到警暴問題?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T14:57:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  點解搵阿差當差你會覺得解決到問題<br />\n又變番1920年代果陣既大頭綠衣，比人笑既年代"},{"pid":"b9e6a2f3772739f88769abed3b9b8f99697fb102","tid":1997023,"uid":74954,"like":0,"disli